asset.author: Victorinox AG
asset.hookText:
The Protect concept has been a signature capsule designed by Christopher Raeburn for Victorinox the past two seasons. For Fall/Winter 2013, this concept is infused throughout the collection and featured in key pieces that exemplify the Futureproof theme. 
The track of the film was made from a combination of acoustic, analogue and digital sound sources. The percussion parts were created from recordings of the various paraphernalia found in Christopher's East London studio as well as recordings of the garments from the Remade in Switzerland collection.

Film by Sam Scott-Hunter and Christopher Raeburn. Music by toot!
